<Base title="SocialProof for Financial Advisors — Client Testimonials That Build Trust | SocialProof" description="Financial advisors: collect and display client testimonials to build credibility with prospects. Turn referrals into conversions. Free to start.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Financial Advisors
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Prospects researching a financial advisor are trusting someone with their retirement, their kids' college fund, their financial future. They research obsessively. Your website with real client testimonials is often the deciding factor between a call and a pass.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">The compliance-friendly testimonial approach</h2>
      <p>Financial advisors often assume testimonials are off-limits due to compliance concerns. But the SEC's 2021 Marketing Rule now permits client testimonials with proper disclosures. SocialProof helps you collect and display compliant testimonials — you retain full editorial control, approving each one before it goes live.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#777;"><em>Note: Always review testimonial content with your compliance team before publishing. SocialProof gives you approval workflows to make this easy.</em></p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">What prospects want to read</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Clarity:</strong> "Finally understand my retirement picture. They explained everything without jargon."</li>
        <li><strong>Peace of mind:</strong> "I sleep better knowing someone with real expertise is watching my portfolio."</li>
        <li><strong>Responsiveness:</strong> "Every question answered within hours. Never feel like a small client."</li>
        <li><strong>Results:</strong> "Our net worth grew 40% in five years. I attribute a lot of that to their planning."</li>
        <li><strong>Relationship:</strong> "They remembered my daughter's college timeline without me mentioning it. That's rare."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for your practice</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Embed the widget</strong> on your homepage, about page, and service pages.</li>
        <li><strong>Send the collection link</strong> after annual reviews, onboarding, or milestone moments.</li>
        <li><strong>Review each testimonial</strong> before publishing — full compliance control in your hands.</li>
        <li><strong>Display credibility</strong> where prospects are evaluating you, 24/7.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Turn referrals into closed clients</h2>
      <p>Financial advisors live on referrals — but referrals still Google you. When a colleague's friend sends someone your way, that person checks your website within hours. A page full of genuine client stories closes the loop that a referral opens. SocialProof bridges the gap between "someone told me about you" and "I booked a call."</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Works for every advisory specialty</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Retirement planning and wealth management</li>
        <li>Tax planning and investment advisory</li>
        <li>Estate and legacy planning</li>
        <li>Business owner financial planning</li>
        <li>Fee-only and fiduciary advisors</li>
        <li>Robo-hybrid and digital wealth platforms</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Free forever for one widget</h2>
      <p>Start collecting financial advisor testimonials today — no credit card required. One widget, unlimited testimonials collected, full approval control.</p>

